{"tid":2279060,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"羅致光：不宜利用關愛基金設立失業援助金","createTime":"2020-11-09T13:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T06:47:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e95e591687e391941b7baed5c504a2f9dd0b62d9","tid":2279060,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:48:12.000Z","msg":"在立法會民政事務委員會，多名議員要求政府動用關愛基金，設立短期失業援助金。勞工及福利局局長羅致光指，撇除80億元的項目承擔額，基金只剩下100億元，認為不宜利用基金設立失業援助金。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員（區議會第二）鄺俊宇：「現時疫情已經差勁，包括零售、市面、失業一直不斷飊升。我們已在很多場合就說，失業援助金是否可由關愛基金上想一想。」<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員邵家輝：「（保就業）月底就會完結。我們初步評估，有些公司都會心灰意冷，都未必一定繼續做下去，或大幅裁減同事。在這情況下如何支援他們，我們之前在不同場合都提出，希望政府有失業綜援。」<br />\n<br />\n羅致光：「保就業計劃每期都四百多億元，我們現時關愛基金所剩下，一個月都做不到。所以，真的要考慮如何幫助個別行業或整體，都是要從防疫抗疫基金上考慮。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412267&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=3908466b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412267&h=9b8a4627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412267</a>"},{"pid":"61a9015801dee64eafd93516362dc07f41724944","tid":2279060,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66959be78d91bd236ae9b35905f5e050c6c09f9","tid":2279060,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"不過佢都係派俾老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71888ae3017b196804e3b5a8def38c010f07d160","tid":2279060,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"港人失業WFC<br />\n<br />\n支那人全職產卵，港共全力支持"},{"pid":"d9fd78aa5ff7f6fb7bc86a0eb169ec5cd5e53eb2","tid":2279060,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"羅致光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}